	1.Launcher界面和主菜单界面可以循环显示????

	解决：
	//packages/apps/Launcher3/ext/src/com/mediatek/launcher3/ext/DefaultWorkspaceExt.java
	@Override
	public boolean supportAppListCycleSliding() {
		return true;		//把这个地方改为 true 就行了
	}

